  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/smartphones/\" rel=\"tag\">智能手机</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/2013/10/22/nokia-lumia-wp8-photo-app-storyteller/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/www.engadget.com/media/2013/10/nokia-world-2013-2013-10-22-4.jpg\" /></a></p>\n\n<p>Nokia 一直自豪于自家移动设备的拍摄能力，现在他们打算帮忙使用者将美好照片串联成美好的故事回忆。而在今天的发表会上不只是有硬件产品的发表而已，随之登场的还有最新的软件 <a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2013/09/29/windows-phone-storyteller-app-screenshot-leak/\">Storyteller app</a> -- 从英文字面上的意义，不难理解它就是一个集结装置内照片与视频，替你编织谈述一次次旅途故事的 App。通过与此 App 同时登场的 Lumia 1520 其四麦克风规格，更是可以将旅途周围的声音尽收手机之中。既然跟旅途相关，使用者将可以通过双指 Zoom out 的动作，来让 Storyteller 以自家的 Nokia Maps 来显示出你照片拍摄地点周边的地图信息。<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/storyteller-offers-new-way-to-view-your-memories-coming-to-nokia-lumia-1520/\">Storyteller offers new way to view your memories, coming to Nokia Lumia 1520</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/storyteller-offers-new-way-to-view-your-memories-coming-to-nokia-lumia-1520/6254646/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/nokia-world-2013-2013-10-22-23-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/storyteller-offers-new-way-to-view-your-memories-coming-to-nokia-lumia-1520/6254653/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/nokia-world-2013-2013-10-22-24-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/storyteller-offers-new-way-to-view-your-memories-coming-to-nokia-lumia-1520/6254659/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/nokia-world-2013-2013-10-22-25-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/storyteller-offers-new-way-to-view-your-memories-coming-to-nokia-lumia-1520/6254661/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/nokia-world-2013-2013-10-22-26-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a></div><br />\n更新：Nokia 也宣布 Storyteller 将会搭载于最新的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/22/nokia-lumia-2520-windows-rt-tablet/\">2520</a> 平板电脑之上。<br />\n<br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/22/nokia-lumia-wp8-photo-app-storyteller/\">Engadget</a></p><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/22/nokia-lumia-wp8-photo-app-storyteller/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20751058/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/22/nokia-lumia-wp8-photo-app-storyteller/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
